{"tid":1161770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不要讓那成爲我們的遺產","createTime":"2019-05-19T12:03:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T19:03:07.000Z","uid":165234,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e106c0b70135bb00c56ad8d48ece3c0ab13bafe0","tid":1161770,"uid":165234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T12:03:33.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">我們被選中<br />\n為世界服務<br />\n<br />\n但是政治<br />\n逼迫我們選擇<br />\n<br />\n這座城市<br />\n孤立無援<br />\n<br />\n有人殊死一搏<br />\n嘗試拯救我們<br />\n<br />\n沒有任何幫助<br />\n他們於監獄中<br />\n<br />\n城市被放棄了<br />\n但更重要的是<br />\n人性也被放棄了<br />\n<br />\n不要讓那成爲我們的遺產<br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"f4053f5208a4dafaa5936b4d1c3ba2ab8906f421","tid":1161770,"uid":198216,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T12:08:58.000Z","msg":"屌中共<br />\n                                      老母"},{"pid":"8cb705f6c08b178dbb5c7c6398054fe400e43f5b","tid":1161770,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T12:23:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef512637906f63f10a97060f201985f837458c41","tid":1161770,"uid":222614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T12:24:43.000Z","msg":"Nice poem <br />\nDo you mind I translate it into English?"},{"pid":"2b6aa280d871712a34e3c006b8bd4edad54461bb","tid":1161770,"uid":20867,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-19T12:29:37.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">我們被選中<br />\n為<span style=\"color: red;\">泛民</span>服務<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">這</span>是政治<br />\n逼迫我們選擇<br />\n<br />\n這座城市<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">全球關注</span><br />\n<br />\n有人殊死一搏<br />\n嘗試<span style=\"color: red;\">改變未來</span><br />\n<br />\n沒有任何幫助<br />\n他們於監獄中<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">青年</span>被放棄了<br />\n但更重要的是<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">真相</span>也被放棄了<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">識事務已</s